Interactions.cross_section_comment:
Cross sections N2.  Same as used in siglo.sec, but extrapolated to 1 kV and minor errors were corrected.
A.V. Phelps and L.C. Pitchford, Phys. Rev. A 31, 2932 (1985);
JILA Information Center Report No. 26, University of Colorado (May 1, 1985).

